+| Web module | Primary route/module consumers | Main backend groups | Notes |
+| --- | --- | --- | --- |
+| `src/api/AuthApi.js` | `Signup`, `Login`, `Otp`, `PersonalDetailsPage`, auth context/profile flows | `/common/*` | Persists traveler profile/session data and keeps app + legacy auth cookies aligned |
+| `src/api/homepageApi.js` | `HomePage` data loaders | `/partner/get_featured_packages/` | Homepage-only featured package loading |
+| `src/api/listingApi.js` | `ListingPage`, listing hooks/components | `/partner/get_package_detail_by_city_and_date/`, `/partner/get_package_short_detail_for_web/` | Powers search/filter driven package discovery |
